

	 
      Here's a good recipe for a skid: a few inches of rain water and muck all over the road. Here I am taking me wife back home from work - one would think a scooter would go nuts and weave all over the place. No sir, not this one. Steady as a rock, this Dio baby is. It just kept tracking where I pointed it. Darn thing was as steady as if it were on rails.  
     
    
